A magnificent view looking up Olive, with, coming at us, the Hillcrest, Angels Flight, and a good-sized chunk of the &lt;a href=&quot;/elksannex&quot; title=&quot;Elx&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;BPOE Lodge&lt;/a&gt;. 
